reviewtext: I've had this keyboard for about 5-6 years now.  I have the Dell verision ("Dell by Microsoft"), which I think is the same as the original Microsoft one,but just has "Dell" branded on the right corner.  It is a good, sturdy keyboard, however, it is very loud.  The other keyboards I have (4 of them) are not half as loud as this one.  I just bought a new Microsoft Erognomic keyboard for my wife, and it is very nice, quiet.
summary: Keyboard works well but VERY LOUD
